---
// Testimonio: versículo arriba + testimonio EJEMPLO abajo.
// El testimonio es ficticio — mostrar el diseño antes de tener uno real.
---

<section class="testimonio" id="impacto">
  <div class="container">
    <!-- Versículo Mateo 5:14 -->
    <div class="quote-mark">"</div>
    <div class="quote">
      Vosotros sois la <span class="highlight">luz</span> del mundo;<br>
      una ciudad asentada sobre un monte<br>
      no se puede esconder.
    </div>
    <div class="cite">— Jesús · Mateo 5:14</div>
  </div>

  <!-- Testimonio EJEMPLO -->
  <div class="container narrow">
    <div class="ejemplo-badge-wrap">
      <span class="ejemplo-badge">⚠ Ejemplo · vista previa del diseño</span>
    </div>

    <div class="testimonial-card">
      <div class="t-photo">
        <img src="/assets/photos/gallery/large/foto_30.jpg" alt="Estudiante de colegio en Costa Rica" loading="lazy" />
      </div>
      <div class="t-content">
        <div class="t-quote-mark">"</div>
        <p class="t-quote">
          Llegué a ese evento sin esperar nada. Salí con una vida diferente.
          La iglesia que LUZ me recomendó ahora es mi familia.
        </p>
        <div class="t-attribution">
          <div class="t-name">María Fernanda, 16 años</div>
          <div class="t-role">Estudiante · Colegio en Heredia</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .testimonio {
    background: var(--charcoal);
    color: var(--on-dark);
    padding: 120px 0;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .testimonio::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    top: -100px;
    left: -100px;
    width: 500px;
    height: 500px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(252,211,77,0.10) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }
  .testimonio::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -100px;
    right: -100px;
    width: 500px;
    height: 500px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(252,211,77,0.06) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .quote-mark {
    font-family: "Fraunces", serif;
    font-size: 120px;
    color: var(--yellow);
    line-height: 0.5;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    opacity: 0.5;
  }
  .quote {
    font-family: "Fraunces", serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: clamp(26px, 4vw, 44px);
    line-height: 1.35;
    color: var(--on-dark);
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto 24px;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }
  .highlight { color: var(--yellow); font-style: normal; font-weight: 600; }
  .cite {
    font-family: "Inter", sans-serif;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--on-dark-soft);
  }

  /* Testimonial card */
  .narrow { max-width: 880px; }
  .ejemplo-badge-wrap {
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 80px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }
  .ejemplo-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 8px 18px;
    background: var(--yellow);
    color: var(--charcoal);
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    border-radius: 100px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(252,211,77,0.25);
  }

  .testimonial-card {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.10);
    border-radius: 24px;
    padding: 36px;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 200px 1fr;
    gap: 36px;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: left;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
  }
  .t-photo {
    width: 200px;
    height: 200px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 4px solid var(--yellow);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
  }
  .t-photo img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
  }
  .t-quote-mark {
    font-family: "Fraunces", serif;
    font-size: 60px;
    color: var(--yellow);
    line-height: 0.5;
    opacity: 0.6;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
  }
  .t-quote {
    font-family: "Fraunces", serif;
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: clamp(20px, 2.4vw, 26px);
    line-height: 1.4;
    color: var(--on-dark);
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    letter-spacing: -0.005em;
  }
  .t-attribution {
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.10);
    padding-top: 14px;
  }
  .t-name {
    font-family: "Inter", sans-serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--yellow);
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }
  .t-role {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--on-dark-soft);
    margin-top: 4px;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
  }

  @media (max-width: 700px) {
    .testimonio { padding: 80px 0; }
    .testimonial-card {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 28px 24px;
    }
    .t-photo { margin: 0 auto; width: 140px; height: 140px; }
    .t-quote-mark { margin: 0 auto 8px; }
    .t-attribution { text-align: center; }
  }
</style>
